jp.go.enri.util.crm.integral

Class LateralOverlapProbability

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.enri.util.crm.integral.LateralOverlapProbability

  • public class LateralOverlapProbability
extends java.lang.Object
    Calculate the lateral overlap probability when the distribution type of TSE is specified. All functions are implemented based on SASP-WG/WHL/11-WP/05 and SASP-WG/WHL/9-WP/14.
    Version:
    1.1 2009/04/21
    2011/11/22
    2013/10/15
    Author:
    Masato Fujita
